sources.title: Lovely Junks 2013
sources.description: Lovely Junks 2013 Synopsis Lovable Trash is the story of an elderly woman who has one night to clear her house of any problematic items during the protests following the presidential elections of 2009. Cast: Hadieh Tehrani, Shahab Hosseini , Negar Javaherian, Saber Abar, Habib Rezaee , Shirin Yazdanbakhsh
